import sys

def main():
    input = sys.stdin.readline().strip()
    N,T,M = input.split(' ')
    N,T,M = int(N),int(T),int(M)
    print(N*T*M)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

N,T,M = [int(x) for x in input().split(' ')]
print(N*T*M)
